description:
UePolicyOptimization:  Table storing UE policy optimization parameters for specific cells, including timestamps, location, UE capabilities, and various optimization settings.

dateTime: Timestamp of the recorded UE policy optimization parameters.
Area_Name: Name of the geographic area where the cell is located.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
Id2: Redundant cell identifier (likely a copy of CellId).
Id3:  Ancillary identifier (purpose unclear from sample data).
vsDataType: Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
UePolicyOptimization.ueCapPrioList: List of prioritized UE capabilities.
UePolicyOptimization.zzzTemporary1: Temporary placeholder column (purpose unclear).
UePolicyOptimization.zzzTemporary2: Temporary placeholder column (purpose unclear).
UePolicyOptimization.zzzTemporary3: Temporary placeholder column (purpose unclear).
UePolicyOptimization.endcAwareImc:  Indicates the mode of ENDC-aware Inter-RAT Mobility Control.
UePolicyOptimization.t320: Value of T320 timer (related to handover).
UePolicyOptimization.uePolicyOptimizationId: Unique identifier for the specific policy optimization configuration.
UePolicyOptimization.coverageAwareImc: Boolean indicating whether coverage-aware Inter-RAT Mobility Control is enabled.
